title: [Karazja Jungle, Overgrown Path]
description: The heavy underbrush thins out slightly as the pathway passes through a stand of tall bamboo trees.  The trees sway in the breeze, rattling and scraping against each other like dry bones.  Patches of open soil appear, revealing a few prints of bare feet in the moist dirt.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, southwest, west, northwest
